label: uncl6321
comment: Code specifying the significance of a measurement.

values.label: Approximately
values.comment: The measurement is approximately equal to that specified.

values.label: Equal to
values.comment: The measurement is equal to that specified.

values.label: Greater than or equal to
values.comment: The measurement is greater than or equal to that specified.

values.label: Greater than
values.comment: The measurement is greater than that specified.

values.label: Less than
values.comment: The measurement is less than that specified.

values.label: Less than or equal to
values.comment: The measurement is less than or equal to that specified.

values.label: Average value
values.comment: Average value for a specific series of readings.

values.label: Not equal to
values.comment: The measurement is not equal to that specified.

values.label: True value
values.comment: The measurement reported is a true value.

values.label: Observed value
values.comment: The measurement reported is an observed value.

values.label: Marked
values.comment: The measurement marked on the object.

values.label: Out of range
values.comment: The measurement reported is out of range.
